[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1011","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1222","title":"微软 Windows NT 4.0 Netbt.sys 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 系统的 Netbt.sys 驱动（负责 NetBIOS over TCP/IP 名称解析）存在拒绝服务漏洞。当系统作为客户端向远程 DNS 服务器发起主机名查询时，若攻击者能够控制或伪造该 DNS 服务器（例如通过中间人攻击或劫持 DNS 响应），使其返回一个 IP 地址为 0.0.0.0 的异常解析结果，Netbt.sys 在处理该非法地址时会触发缺陷，导致系统崩溃并停止响应。该漏洞仅影响 Windows NT 4.0 操作系统，攻击条件为攻击者能够向目标主机返回恶意构造的 DNS 解析响应，利用方式是通过操纵 DNS 服务器返回 0.0.0.0 地址以引发远程拒绝服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1222"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:58.753","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本（如 Windows 2000/XP/Server 2003），并应用微软安全公告 MS99-037 发布的补丁（Q269874）。若无法立即升级，请在防火墙层面限制仅允许受信任的 DNS 服务器（如企业内部 DNS），禁止外部 DNS 解析请求，并在主机防火墙层面禁止 NetBIOS over TCP/IP（NetBT）协议端口（UDP/TCP 137、138、139、445）对外暴露，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q188/5/71.ASP","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3893","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1222.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1222","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1222.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f298f72e4ec0bc0f6b7151db8bb167727c83d2d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1222.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2wcg-78mh-f9m8/GHSA-2wcg-78mh-f9m8.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87559/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1222.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001008.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1011.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1010","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1010.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1206","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10819,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10841}}","description":"该漏洞存在于 SystemSoft SystemWizard 软件包中，该软件包在 HP Pavilion PC 以及可能的其他平台和操作系统（如 Windows 98）上安装时，会创建两个被标记为可安全脚本的 ActiveX 控件。攻击者可以通过引用这些控件（包括 Launch 控制和 RegObj 控制）来构造恶意网页，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。由于这些控件的安全标记 bypassed，攻击者无需任何身份验证即可远程触发此漏洞。漏洞影响范围广泛，不仅限于 HP Pavilion PC，可能涉及其他安装了 SystemWizard 的平台。此外，两个 ActiveX 控件（Launch 控制和 RegObj 控制）中的任意一个都能被利用，为攻击提供了两种途径。这一漏洞允许攻击者在目标计算机上执行任意代码，可能导致系统完整性受损、数据泄露或进一步的攻击扩散。目前尚未有针对此漏洞的官方补丁，但 Microsoft 建议禁用不信任的 ActiveX 控件或使用最新安全更新以减轻风险。攻击者可以通过在目标系统上加载恶意的网页或内容来触发此漏洞，只要用户访问了包含恶意引用的网页即可，而无需用户的任何交互或权限提升。攻击可以通过在浏览器中加载自定义网页来实现，当网页包含对这两个 ActiveX 控件的引用时，系统将自动尝试执行这些控件的安全脚本，从而允许攻击者注入和执行任意代码。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1206"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:56.753","remediation":"建议立即卸载 HP Pavilion 预装的 SystemSoft SystemWizard 包，或在 Internet Explorer 中将\"对未标记为可安全执行脚本的 ActiveX 控件初始化并执行脚本\"设置为\"禁用\"，并在\"受信任站点\"区域移除不受信任站点。如无法卸载，可在注册表中删除 Launch 和 RegObj 两个 ActiveX 控件的 CLSID 键值（HKCR\\\\CLSID\\\\{...}）以禁用其脚本调用。建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本以彻底消除该漏洞风险。作为临时缓解，可在防火墙层面阻断恶意网页访问或禁用 ActiveX 控件运行权限。建议参考 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-032 及 HP 安全公告获取补丁补丁包进行彻底修复。升级至 Windows 2000 SP4 或更高版本可彻底消除该漏洞风险。建议卸载 SystemWizard 组件或在注册表中删除相关 ActiveX 控件的 CLSID 键值（HKCR\\\\CLSID\\\\{...}）。作为临时缓解，可在 IE 安全设置中将\"对未标记为安全的 ActiveX 控件初始化并执行脚本\"设为\"禁用\"，并在受信任站点区域移除不可信站点。建议参考 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-032 应用补丁或升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本彻底修复。作为临时缓解措施，可在防火墙层面阻断恶意网页访问或禁用 ActiveX 控件运行权限。建议卸载 SystemSoft SystemWizard 包或在注册表中删除 Launch 和 RegObj 两个 ActiveX 控件的 CLSID 键值以禁用其脚本调用能力。升级至 Windows 2000 SP4 或更高版本可彻底消除该漏洞风险。建议参考 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-032 及 HP 安全公告应用补丁或升级系统。作为临时缓解，可在 IE 安全设置中禁用\"对未标记为安全的 ActiveX 控件初始化并执行脚本\"并在受信任站点区域移除不可信站点。升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本可彻底消除该漏洞风险。建议卸载 SystemWizard 组件或删除相关 ActiveX 控件 CLSID 注册表键值。作为临时缓解，可在 IE 安全设置中禁用 ActiveX 控件脚本执行权限。参考 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-032 应用补丁或升级系统版本彻底修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93336970231857&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/555","http://www.systemsoft.com/l-2/l-3/support-systemwizard.htm","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1206.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1206","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1206.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f298f72e4ec0bc0f6b7151db8bb167727c83d2d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1206.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gjmg-cjcp-mhwg/GHSA-gjmg-cjcp-mhwg.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/555/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1206.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001007.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1010.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1002","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1177","title":"Nph-publish 目录遍历任意文件写入漏洞","description":"nph-publish 1.2 之前版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者在文件上传操作的路径名中使用 `..`（点点）目录遍历序列，可绕过路径限制以 Web 服务器权限覆盖任意文件。攻击者可通过上传恶意脚本覆盖关键文件导致远程代码执行或服务中断，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1177"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.990","remediation":"立即升级 nph-publish 至 1.2 或更高版本（下载地址：http://stein.cshl.org/~lstein/server_publish/）。如无法升级，直接删除或移除 nph-publish 脚本的执行权限（chmod -x nph-publish）。同时确保 Web 服务器以最低权限用户（非 root）运行，并将上传目标目录权限设置为非全局可写，避免攻击者利用目录遍历覆盖任意文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www-genome.wi.mit.edu/WWW/tools/CGI_scripts/server_publish/nph-publish","http://www.w3.org/Security/Faq/wwwsf4.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2055","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/1999/CVE-1999-1177.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/928db9679b69032a137f1c2f3374c28367145ef0/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1177.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-1177.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1177","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1177.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-1999-1177.yaml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v755-q23g-3hrx/GHSA-v755-q23g-3hrx.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1177.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/nph-publish.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1002.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1002.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1001","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1175","title":"Cisco IOS Cache Engine Web Cache Control Protocol 认证漏洞","description":"tags.<value>Cisco IOS 11.2 及更早版本所配套的 Cisco Cache Engine 在实现 Web 缓存控制协议（WCCP）时未引入任何认证机制。WCCP 通过 UDP 2048 端口通信，用于协调缓存引擎与路由器之间的流量重定向。由于协议缺乏身份校验，未经过认证的远程攻击者可向目标路由器的 UDP 2048 端口伪造并发送 WCCP 报文，从而将经过该设备的 HTTP 流量重定向至攻击者可控的任意主机，进而实施中间人劫持、流量监听或钓鱼攻击。该漏洞影响运行 Cisco IOS 11.2 及更早版本且启用 WCCP 功能的 Cisco 网络设备与缓存引擎，攻击只需网络可达目标 UDP 2048 端口，无需本地权限或用户交互，利用门槛低、危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1175"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.753","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 11.3 或更高版本以启用 WCCP 身份验证功能；若暂时无法升级，请在路由器上执行 \"no ip wccp\" 命令禁用 WCCP 服务，或在防火墙层面阻断 UDP 2048 端口防止未授权流量重定向。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-054.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/wccpauth-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1577","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/1999/CVE-1999-1175.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/928db9679b69032a137f1c2f3374c28367145ef0/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1175.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1175","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1175.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1175.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2qg5-3mg4-mrr4/GHSA-2qg5-3mg4-mrr4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1175.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/C/cisco-sa-19980513-wccp-auth.nasl","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001005.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--71565265-4d4c-43b5-9801-c1bbf5c6174a.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0996","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0996.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1167","title":"Third Voice Web Annotation 跨站脚本漏洞","description":"Third Voice Web Annotation 注释工具存在跨站脚本（XSS）漏洞。远程攻击者可在网页注释中注入恶意 JavaScript 代码，当其他 Third Voice 用户浏览同一页面并加载注释时，恶意脚本将在用户浏览器中自动执行，导致攻击者可窃取用户 Cookie 及敏感数据，或伪造网页内容实施钓鱼攻击。该漏洞影响 Third Voice 注释扩展所有版本，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。用户需警惕不明来源注释，建议卸载该软件以消除风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1167"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.783","remediation":"立即卸载 Third Voice 软件（该产品已停止维护，于 2000 年左右退出市场且不再发布安全更新）。在浏览器扩展管理中移除所有 Third Voice 相关插件。替代方案：使用现代浏览器内置注释功能或基于服务端的内容注释工具（如 Hypothes.is），这些方案默认对用户输入进行转义处理并实施 CSP 策略，可有效防范 XSS 攻击。如需继续使用第三方注释系统，应启用 Content-Security-Policy HTTP 头并配置 `script-src` 限制内联脚本执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7252.php","http://www.wired.com/news/technology/0%2C1282%2C20636%2C00.html","http://www.wired.com/news/technology/0%2C1282%2C20677%2C00.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d39c6fc359564f87c4fbc1b2c3e7c679c878fdd9/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1167.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1167","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1167.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/b61a9cff022af7967458616078d0be1725a7f46a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1167.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qgpq-pjxc-x5wq/GHSA-qgpq-pjxc-x5wq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83040/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1167.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e64526992db40c94520d0244d04a3aa859684904/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0996.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0988","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0988.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1157","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 ICMP 子网掩码请求拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的 tcpip.sys 在处理 ICMP Subnet Mask Address Request 数据包时存在缺陷，当多个 IP 地址绑定到同一网络接口时，远程攻击者可通过发送特制的 ICMP 子网掩码请求报文触发该漏洞，导致目标系统服务崩溃。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 SP4 之前版本，需目标配置多 IP 绑定环境，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1157"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:50.523","remediation":"建议安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 (SP4) 或更高版本，SP4 已修复了 tcpip.sys 对 ICMP Subnet Mask 请求处理不当导致的拒绝服务问题。临时缓解方案：在边界防火墙上过滤入站 ICMP 类型 17 代码 0（子网掩码请求）数据包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q192/7/74.ASP","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3894"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0988.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0978","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0978.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1132","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Routing Information Field 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 在处理令牌环网络中的源路由数据时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，向目标系统发送特制的 Routing Information Field（RIF）数据包，构造跳数超过 7 的冗余路由条目，或包含重复的 Token Ring ID，即可触发内核错误，导致目标系统蓝屏崩溃。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 系列操作系统，攻击成本低、无需用户交互，属于中等危害的拒绝服务漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1132"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:47.313","remediation":"根本修复方案：由于 Windows NT 4.0 已终止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019 或 2022）。临时缓解措施：在网络边界防火墙或路由器上配置 ACL 规则，丢弃源路由选项（Source Routing）数据包，阻止含有异常 RIF 跳数（>7）或重复 Token Ring ID 的 Token Ring 源路由帧进入内部网络。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90763508011966&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=90760603030452&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q179/1/57.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/1399.php"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0978.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0963","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0963.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1126","title":"Cisco Resource Manager 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cisco Resource Manager (CRM) 1.1 及更早版本创建文件时使用了不安全的权限设置，导致本地攻击者可读取 swim_swd.log、swim_debug.log、dbi_debug.log 以及名称以 \"DPR_\" 开头的临时文件，从中获取包含用户名、密码和 SNMP 团体字串在内的敏感配置信息。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，但需要系统本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1126"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.547","remediation":"将 Cisco Resource Manager 升级至 CiscoWorks Resource Manager Essentials (RME) 后续受支持版本；同时立即对 swim_swd.log、swim_debug.log、dbi_debug.log 及 DPR_* 临时文件设置仅 root 可读权限（chmod 600），并清除日志中明文存储的用户名、密码及 SNMP 团体字串；限制仅授权管理员具有本地系统访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-086.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/crmtmp-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1575","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1126.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1126","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1126.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1126.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1126.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87017/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1126.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ea4986e5-e053-4e4f-b784-9c4adf62a083.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idinfor"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0963.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0959","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0959.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1124","title":"Adobe ColdFusion HTTP客户端安全绕过漏洞","description":"Allaire ColdFusion 中的 mainframeset.cfm 页面存在安全绕过漏洞。该页面提供的 HTTP 客户端功能允许远程攻击者提交目标 URL，服务器会代表攻击者向内网其他端口上的 Web 页面发起请求，由于请求来源被伪造为本地回环地址（localhost），因此可以绕过基于 IP 地址或端口的访问控制策略。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞扫描内网端口、访问内部受限资源，导致敏感信息泄露或进一步的横向攻击。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1124"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.283","remediation":"升级至 ColdFusion 5.0 或更高版本（该版本修复了 mainframeset.cfm SSRF 绕过问题）；若无法升级，在 Web 服务器（IIS/Apache）层面通过 URL 重写规则或访问控制列表（ACL）禁止外部请求访问 /mainframeset.cfm 路径；同时在防火墙上限制应用服务器对外部端口的出站连接，防止被利用为内网探测代理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstorm.securify.com/mag/phrack/phrack54/P54-08","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1124","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1124.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c8gw-jg28-8m4v/GHSA-c8gw-jg28-8m4v.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/7ae10c2036875bb5ef530e18322e7ca2477ed16c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0959.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0957","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0957.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1117","title":"IBM AIX lquerypv 本地文件读取漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1 及 4.2 系统中的 lquerypv 工具在解析 -h 命令行参数时未对文件路径进行充分校验，导致存在任意文件读取漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 -h 参数传入目标文件路径（如 /etc/passwd 或系统配置文件），越权读取本无权访问的敏感文件内容，造成信息泄露。该漏洞利用条件要求攻击者拥有本地 shell 访问权限，虽然无需 root 权限但无法远程触发，故整体危害较低，CVSS 评分 2.1。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1117"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:45.383","remediation":"升级 IBM AIX 至 4.3 或更高版本，IBM 已通过 APAR 修复此问题。如无法升级，以 root 执行 `chmod 755 /usr/sbin/lquerypv` 移除 setuid 权限，阻止普通用户以特权运行该命令。同时通过文件系统 ACL 限制可执行 `lquerypv` 的用户范围作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/h-13.shtml","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420195&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420196&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&w=2&r=1&s=lquerypv&q=b","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/455","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1752","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19345","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1117","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1117.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g9xm-g3q5-pm76/GHSA-g9xm-g3q5-pm76.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000997.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0957.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0947","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0947.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1105","title":"Microsoft Windows 95 远程任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Windows 95 在启用 NetWare 网络的远程管理和文件共享功能时存在设计缺陷，当管理员远程登录系统后会自动创建隐藏的 C$ 共享目录，且未对共享访问权限进行有效限制。远程攻击者无需高级权限，只需通过网络映射该驱动器即可读取目标系统上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 操作系统，利用方式简单，危害主要为信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1105"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.947","remediation":"立即禁用 Remote Administration 和 File Sharing for NetWare Networks 功能（进入控制面板 → 网络 → 服务，移除 File and Printer Sharing for NetWare Networks 及相关绑定）。由于 Windows 95 已终止支持，建议尽快迁移至受支持的 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 版本，并确保 SMB 服务不暴露于公网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7231.php","http://www.net-security.sk/bugs/NT/netware1.html","http://www.zdnet.com/eweek/reviews/1016/tr42bug.html","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1105.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1105.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1105.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1105.json","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/8fb60f1e10e801132244052aaca5ef57fba4fd01/1999/CVE-1999-1105.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rcfw-38c9-2wm8/GHSA-rcfw-38c9-2wm8.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1105","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88095/info.html","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1105.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1105.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0947.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0944","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0944.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1104","title":"Microsoft Windows 95 密码列表文件弱加密权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows 95 在启用密码缓存时对密码列表（.pwl）文件使用弱加密算法进行存储，本地攻击者可通过直接访问该文件并利用加密缺陷破译其中的明文密码，从而获取系统登录凭据并提升自身权限。该漏洞影响所有启用密码缓存的 Windows 95 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。微软已发布相关安全公告。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1104"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.830","remediation":"Windows 95 已停止支持且无官方安全更新。建议立即禁用密码缓存：打开控制面板 → 密码 → 更改密码 → 点击\"开始使用\"并取消勾选所有密码缓存选项，同时删除 %WINDIR% 目录下所有 .pwl 文件。作为根本解决方案，应升级至仍受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11）以消除此风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167418931&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88536273725787&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=88540877601866&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q140/5/57.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/71.php","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1104.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1104.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1104","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1104.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1104.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wmcw-55j3-3jh6/GHSA-wmcw-55j3-3jh6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1104.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000995.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0944.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0942","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0942.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1102","title":"BSD lpr 本地任意文件写入漏洞","description":"BSD 系统中 lpr 打印服务组件存在任意文件写入漏洞，本地攻击者可通过符号链接（symlink）攻击方式，在多次调用 lpr 命令（约 1000 次）后触发竞争条件，导致以 lp 权限创建或覆盖系统任意文件。该漏洞影响 SunOS 4.1.1、BSD 4.3、A/UX 2.0.1 及其他基于 BSD 的操作系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1102"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.580","remediation":"建议升级至现代 BSD 发行版（FreeBSD 4.0+/OpenBSD 2.0+）或改用 CUPS 替代 lpr 打印系统。如因兼容性无法升级，可通过移除 lpr 的 setuid 权限作为临时缓解：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/lpr`，但会限制普通用户使用打印功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/e-25.shtml","http://www.aenigma.net/resources/maillist/bugtraq/1994/0091.htm","http://www.phreak.org/archives/security/8lgm/8lgm.lpr","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1102.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1102","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1102.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1102.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1102.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-97ch-49wx-wfmx/GHSA-97ch-49wx-wfmx.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88452/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000994.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1102.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0942.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0940","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0940.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1100","title":"Cisco PIX Private Link 配置文件加密漏洞","description":"Cisco PIX Private Link 4.1.6及更早版本在处理配置文件中的特定命令时存在加密强度削弱漏洞，导致 DES 密钥有效长度从标准 56 位降低至 48 位。攻击者可利用该弱点对加密通信实施暴力破解，从而获取敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Cisco PIX 防火墙设备的 Private Link 功能，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商已发布安全公告并提供修复建议。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1100"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.327","remediation":"升级 Cisco PIX Private Link 至 4.2 及以上版本，其中已修复 DES 密钥处理逻辑，恢复完整密钥长度。如无法升级或产品已停服，应将加密方案迁移至 AES（如 IPsec 配置中改用 AES-128/256），弃用 DES 算法；同时在防火墙 ACL 中限制可访问 PIX Private Link 管理接口的源 IP 范围，减少暴力破解攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-056.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/pixkey-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1579","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1100.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1100.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1100","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1100.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1100.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1100.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mv5q-6rw5-rqwv/GHSA-mv5q-6rw5-rqwv.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1100.json","https://github.com/robinzixuan/attackmap/blob/3e50ba1e011308b7d6ea18a627132f0a357f36c0/Asia/bruteresult.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0940.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0936","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0936.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1093","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer JScript 脚本引擎缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.01 SP1 及更早版本的 JScript 脚本引擎中的 Window.External 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过诱导用户访问特制恶意网页触发该漏洞，利用缓冲区溢出执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 IE 4.01 SP1 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中危。用户应升级浏览器版本或避免访问不可信网页以降低风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1093"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.420","remediation":"升级 Internet Explorer 至 4.01 SP2 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。建议将浏览器升级至 IE 5.01 SP4 或 IE 6.0 SP1 以彻底消除风险。如已停止使用 IE 老旧版本，应迁移至 Edge 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q191/2/00.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/1276.php","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us